	Script Named:  Decode EHR Bridge RESTful Service Response
	Created:		Jeffrey Ritz
	Date: 		2022-03-03
	Desc:		The purpose of this script is to decode the Base64 encoded RESTful response payload from the EHR Bridge response
	History:
*/
